    |Route: 
    br
    | Adventist Hospital --> Ha Fa Shan --> Shek Lung Kung -->
    | Tin Fu Tsai --> Wing Kat Bridge --> Kat Hing Bridge -->
    | Tai Tong Country Park --> Tai Tong Village
